descriptionHtml:
Puppy Paws is 7,000 square feet of fun Daycare & Dog Nanny that will parallel your dog’s natural instincts, ensuring the highest level of health and safety for dogs of all shapes and sizes. New air filtration system, 4 indoor play parks and 6,000 SF of outdoor play space, a Puppy Paws training classroom, and luxury sleep suites all combined to create the most exclusive, state-of-the art dog care and dog boarding facility in Edmond Oklahoma.

In providing our paw-fect daycare, boarding, grooming, and training services, our pet hospitality business only has your dogs’ happiness and welfare in mind. A locally owned business, we offer top-standard pet accommodation that uniquely blends a homelike atmosphere with an upscale facility that promotes recreational activity.
